1 plan and
2 (1) Grants grants access to the healthcare insurer's contracting
3 entity's provider network or healthcare contract to another healthcare
4 insurer or entity that is:
5 (A) An affiliate of the healthcare insurer; or
6 (B) Operating according to the same brand licensee program
7 as the healthcare insurer; or
8 (2) A contracting entity:
9 (2)(A) Provides notice of the intent to lease, rent, or
10 sell a healthcare contract or provider network of a health benefit plan to
11 another healthcare insurer or third-party administrator;
12 (3)(B) Allows a healthcare provider that is a party to the
13 healthcare contract or provider network of a health benefit plan the
14 opportunity to opt out of participating in the:
15 (A)(i) Proposed lease, rental, or sale of a
16 healthcare contract or provider network of a health benefit plan entirely
17 upon the execution or renewal of the healthcare contract; and
18 (B)(ii) Lease, rental, or sale of a healthcare
19 contract with respect to an individual contracting entity, healthcare
20 insurer, or third-party administrator upon notice that the individual
21 contracting entity, healthcare insurer, or third-party administrator has
22 violated the terms of the healthcare contract; and
23 (4)(C) Provides contact information for the healthcare
