4 SECTION 4. Arkansas Code Title 23, Chapter 99, Subchapter 12, is
5 amended to add an additional section to read as follows:
6 23-99-1211. Waiver prohibited.
7 (a) This subchapter shall not be waived by contract.
8 (b) A contractual arrangement or action taken in conflict with this
9 subchapter or that purports to waive a requirement of this subchapter is
10 void.
